    (26, 79, 'name=>pageDefault;value=>20', 'set grid page size (default=20). Valid values: 10,20,50,100\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Set global default (for all grids) in pef_setting.</li>\r\n    <li>Tip - for grids that will never have many rows: set pageDefault and hide the footer</li>\r\n</ul>', 'dcd26-dib'),
